# Vue Component Rules

- Always use `<script setup lang="ts">` — no Options API.
- Type props: `defineProps<{ title: string; count?: number }>()`.
- Type emits: `defineEmits<{ (e: 'update', id: string): void }>()`.
- Keep under ~150 lines. Extract sub-components if larger.
- Do NOT manually import auto-imported APIs: `ref`, `computed`, `watch`, `useRoute`, `navigateTo`, `$fetch`.
- DO explicitly import: Pinia stores (`import { useItemsStore } from '~/stores/items'`), shared types (`import type { Item } from '~/shared/types'`).
- Use Tailwind utility classes with design tokens from `@theme`. No inline styles, no raw hex colors.
- Use `:focus-visible` (not `:focus`) for focus states.
- Phosphor Icons only, light weight, via `currentColor`.
